h3c-sgbox-translator (2.0.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Major release: async rewrite with 3rd-party dependencies
  * Replaced stdlib http.server with aiohttp async web framework
  * Added uvloop for high-performance event loop
  * Added structlog for structured JSON logging
  * Added tenacity for retry logic with exponential backoff
  * Added pyOpenSSL for enhanced TLS certificate handling
  * Made syslog forwarder fully async (asyncio streams)
  * Made API server fully async (aiohttp middlewares)
  * Requires Python >= 3.11 (Debian 13 Trixie default)
  * Removed all Python 3.6 compatibility code

 -- H3C Translator Team <admin@example.com>  Sun, 23 Mar 2026 11:30:00 +0200
